    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="github代码提交流程"><a href="#github代码提交流程" class="headerlink" title="github代码提交流程"></a>github代码提交流程</h2><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br><span class="line">12</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git init</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">git add 文件名字</span><br><span class="line">git commit -m  &quot;注释内容&quot;</span><br><span class="line">git remote add 仓库名字 仓库地址</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">#</span><span class="language-bash">git <span class="built_in">rm</span> 文件名 <span class="comment">#本地倒库内删除</span></span> </span><br><span class="line">git config --global http.proxy http://127.0.0.1:端口号</span><br><span class="line">git config --global https.proxy http://127.0.0.1:端口号</span><br><span class="line">git push -u 仓库名字</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config user.name &quot;new name&quot;</span><br><span class="line">git config credential.username &quot;new name&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git rm -r sm3_加速</span><br><span class="line">git commit -m &quot;删除说明&quot;</span><br><span class="line">git push</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git pull practice master</span><br><span class="line"><span class="meta prompt_">#</span><span class="language-bash">每次提交前先pull一下</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h5 id="1-rejected-master-gt-master-non-fast-forward-解决方案："><a href="#1-rejected-master-gt-master-non-fast-forward-解决方案：" class="headerlink" title="1.! [rejected] master -&gt; master (non-fast-forward)解决方案："></a>1.! [rejected] master -&gt; master (non-fast-forward)解决方案：</h5><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/zyz00000000/article/details/84402189">https://blog.csdn.net/zyz00000000/article/details/84402189</a></p><p>2.删除文件夹</p><p><a href="https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_45309916/article/details/108275311">https://blog.csdn.net/weixin_45309916/article/details/108275311</a></p>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
